{"tid":1369620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］ 推到有巴絲設計小輩圖教育未來棟樑，我地始終會老嫁","createTime":"2019-07-26T17:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T03:06:02.000Z","uid":253438,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3acd99262bfd3d637cd515291c7c554c5852e4b1","tid":1369620,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:47:25.000Z","msg":"蓮花加一生平安長輩圖已經周街有<br />\n教育完藍絲長輩<br />\n裝飾香港時同巴絲傾開<br />\n依家係時候教育白紙一張嘅小輩！<br />\n<br />\n其實啲小朋友行天橋、行街真係兩頭望<br />\n咁佢哋嘅視線就係剛剛好望啲欄杆咁<br />\n而且見到啲得意嘅嘢佢哋實會想知係咩黎<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">求有畫卡通/兒童插畫靚嘅巴絲<br />\n設計一D小輩圖比大家裝飾香港<br />\n簡單海報或者故事形式嘅都好好</span><br />\n教育我哋嘅下一代<br />\n唔洗做港豬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2047我地都老了<br />\n將來香港有咩事有佢地接力</span><br />\n<br />\n金鐘播種 遍地開花<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c823b95ea2af995451c894e9f775d21836f7ab0c","tid":1369620,"uid":253438,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:49:20.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"bd8ec3467850589fb06a0fbb87a5148e7750e8e5","tid":1369620,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:50:56.000Z","msg":"自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3b6e071feaf2354986e933dc138507c2efa8fe","tid":1369620,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:52:04.000Z","msg":"有用post 求幫推"},{"pid":"2b27203dc57e9dd16b79ec867c625918f01a589d","tid":1369620,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:53:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1facbbada